description:
In this Study Hall we were joined by one of the most powerful women in Venture Capital. Megan Holston-Alexander is a one of the most successful V.C. firms ever Andreessen Horowitz. She leads the firm's Cultural Leadership Fund (CLF). 

She covered venture capital, and her journey in Silicon Valley. #vc #venturecapital #business
